Digital card:
For each Debit Card the client has a Digital Card associated. 
 Just follow these simple instructions: 
 1. Select your account; 
 2. Select the image of the 'Digital Card' (on the upper right side); 
 3. Enter your 'App Security Key' and you will access your Digital Card; 
 4. Your CVV3 security code will change every five minutes for greater security in your purchases.
